<!DOCTYPE topic SYSTEM "mingle_help.dtd">
<topic title="Edit profile page">
	<section title="What you can do on this page">
	<p>The Edit profile page lets you view and change details of your Mingle sign-in profile, and also the setting of your <cref topic="explore_mingle_page">Explore Mingle tab</cref>.</p>
	<note><cref topic="user_roles#mingle_administrator">Mingle administrators</cref> can edit any user's profile</note>
	</section>
	<section title="Edit your profile details" collapsed = 'true'>
		<p>You can update the following information:</p>
		<bullets>
			<item>Personal Icon</item>
			<item>Sign-in name</item>
			<item>Display name</item>
			<item>Email address</item>
			<item>Jabber user name</item>
			<item>Version control name</item>
		</bullets>
		<p><screenshot src="resources/images/edit_profile.png" /></p>
		<note>You can use <strong>&#43;</strong>, <strong>&#46;</strong>, <strong>&#45;</strong>, <strong>&#64;</strong> and <strong>&#95;</strong> in your display name.</note>
	</section>
	<section title="Non-essential profile details" file="non_essential_profile_details" collapsed="true"/>
	<section title="Hide/Show Explore Mingle tab" collapsed = 'true'>
		<p>You can choose to show or hide your <cref topic="explore_mingle_page">Explore Mingle tab</cref> by using the <strong>Display "Explore Mingle"</strong> checkbox.</p>
		<screenshot alttext="Select Explore Mingle checkbox" src="resources/images/edit_profile_explore_mingle_checkbox.png" />
	</section>
	<section title="Also see...">
		<bullets>
			<item><cref topic="user_roles">About Mingle user roles</cref></item>
			<item><cref topic="creating_user_profiles">Creating users (Mingle administrator)</cref></item>
			<item><cref topic="managing_project_team_members">Managing project team members (project administrator)</cref></item>
			<item><cref topic="managing_your_user_profile">Managing your user profile</cref></item>
		</bullets>
	</section>
</topic>


